* Modern Carlist groups are:
** Partido Carlista Official page of the Carlist Party, recognizes Carlos Hugo&#x27;s son as heir, but follows the leftist ideology many Carlists reject
** Comunión Catolico-Monarquica Official page of the Charles VIII Communion, supporting Dominic von Habsburg as claimant
** Comunión Tradicionalista Carlista Official page of the Carlist Traditionalist Communion. Does not formally endorse any claimant
** Comunión Tradicionalista Official page of the Traditionalist Communion officially supporting Sixtus Henry as regent, also rejects leftist ideology
